The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Arun Lal for Jharkhand

A STAFF REPORTER

Calcutta: Former India opener Arun Lal, who has been approached by Jharkhand Cricket Association (JCA) to train their cricketers during the off-season, will be accompanied by trainer Naseem and Eastern Railway Sports Association (ERSA) wicketkeeper-batsman Rahul Dev. 

Lal is scheduled to leave the city in a couple of days. 




